name: JimMassey'sCleaners
0:
”Alexa, open Jim Massey's Cleaners”
”Alexa, tell Jim Massey's Cleaners I am on my way”
”Alexa, ask Jim Massey's Cleaners to pick up my clothes.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: jim massey's cleaners
Developer Terms of Use
des: Dry cleaning and laundry has never been easier! Simply have Alexa tell Jim Massey that "I'm on my way" and all of your clothes will be pulled, ready and waiting for you when you come in. You can even ask to have Jim Massey schedule a free route pickup and Alexa will let you know when your next driver will be by. The Jim Massey Alexa skill is indeed the easiest way to dry clean.
